&lt;p&gt;The incumbent will operate as a key component of the European Sales Team, identifying prospects, driving campaigns and new business plans and existing account plans to generate a substantive pipeline that delivers revenue growth (annual contract value) in line with or ahead of personal quotas. In addition to direct sales, the Senior Business Development Manager’s role will also include market expansion through close collaboration and leveraging opportunities within the partner ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
